---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components"
---

<section id="problema" class="py-20 bg-surface relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-12">
                Sinais de que seu site foi abandonado 
            </h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div
                    class="bg-black/60 border border-red-500/20 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:border-red-500/40 transition-colors text-center"
                >
                    <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                            <Icon name="lucide:turtle" class="w-8 h-8 text-red-500" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Lentidão extrema</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        O cliente clica e desiste antes de abrir. Você paga tráfego para jogar fora porque a página não carrega
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="bg-black/60 border border-red-500/20 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:border-red-500/40 transition-colors text-center"
                >
                    <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                            <Icon name="lucide:smartphone-nfc" class="w-8 h-8 text-red-500" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Quebrado no Celular</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Botões que não funcionam, textos ilegíveis, layout bagunçado. Experiência amadora que queima sua marca
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="bg-black/60 border border-red-500/20 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:border-red-500/40 transition-colors text-center"
                >
                    <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-500/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                            <Icon name="lucide:ghost" class="w-8 h-8 text-red-500" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Sem Suporte</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                        Quem fez sumiu. Você tem medo de mexer e quebrar tudo. O site virou um "zumbi" digital
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
